Assets.Name: Truro Plaza
Assets.Description:
Hi everyone, I'm proud to release Truro Plaza Skatepark for Session so you can all experience one of my local skateparks. This park offers a large number of gaps and ledges which work really well with Sessions physics. Tag me in any edits or lines so I can see, and most of all enjoy this map

And as a side note if this is one of the first parks you're downloading, make sure to cap the FPS to 60 or 90 to avoid a weird rotating board that happens when you have an extremely high framerate

Assets.Name: Modular Seaside Town
Assets.Description:
Modular Seaside Town v2

This map is still a modified version of the free Marketplace map of the same name on the Epic Unreal Engine Marketplace. It was created by Vytautas Katarzis. https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/slug/modular-seaside-town

v2 fixes most of the floating collision which was a common complaint.

Fixed shadows disappearing on medium or low, requires restarting Session after changing the graphics settings

Finished the small overlook spot.

Added another palm tree model and wind animation to them.

Known bugs: The water foam texture does not load

This is likely the final release of this map unless I can figure out how to fix the broken texture.
